snippets.title: DocumentProcessorService processDocument Sample
snippets.description: Processes a single document.

snippets.title: DocumentProcessorService batchProcessDocuments Sample
snippets.description: LRO endpoint to batch process many documents. The output is written to Cloud Storage as JSON in the [Document] format.

snippets.title: DocumentProcessorService fetchProcessorTypes Sample
snippets.description: Fetches processor types. Note that we don't use [ListProcessorTypes][google.cloud.documentai.v1beta3.DocumentProcessorService.ListProcessorTypes] here, because it isn't paginated.

snippets.title: DocumentProcessorService listProcessorTypes Sample
snippets.description: Lists the processor types that exist.

snippets.title: DocumentProcessorService getProcessorType Sample
snippets.description: Gets a processor type detail.

snippets.title: DocumentProcessorService listProcessors Sample
snippets.description: Lists all processors which belong to this project.

snippets.title: DocumentProcessorService getProcessor Sample
snippets.description: Gets a processor detail.

snippets.title: DocumentProcessorService trainProcessorVersion Sample
snippets.description: Trains a new processor version. Operation metadata is returned as [TrainProcessorVersionMetadata][google.cloud.documentai.v1beta3.TrainProcessorVersionMetadata].

snippets.title: DocumentProcessorService getProcessorVersion Sample
snippets.description: Gets a processor version detail.

snippets.title: DocumentProcessorService listProcessorVersions Sample
snippets.description: Lists all versions of a processor.

snippets.title: DocumentProcessorService deleteProcessorVersion Sample
snippets.description: Deletes the processor version, all artifacts under the processor version will be deleted.

snippets.title: DocumentProcessorService deployProcessorVersion Sample
snippets.description: Deploys the processor version.

snippets.title: DocumentProcessorService undeployProcessorVersion Sample
snippets.description: Undeploys the processor version.

snippets.title: DocumentProcessorService createProcessor Sample
snippets.description: Creates a processor from the [ProcessorType][google.cloud.documentai.v1beta3.ProcessorType] provided. The processor will be at `ENABLED` state by default after its creation.

snippets.title: DocumentProcessorService deleteProcessor Sample
snippets.description: Deletes the processor, unloads all deployed model artifacts if it was enabled and then deletes all artifacts associated with this processor.

snippets.title: DocumentProcessorService enableProcessor Sample
snippets.description: Enables a processor

snippets.title: DocumentProcessorService disableProcessor Sample
snippets.description: Disables a processor

snippets.title: DocumentProcessorService setDefaultProcessorVersion Sample
snippets.description: Set the default (active) version of a [Processor][google.cloud.documentai.v1beta3.Processor] that will be used in [ProcessDocument][google.cloud.documentai.v1beta3.DocumentProcessorService.ProcessDocument] and [BatchProcessDocuments][google.cloud.documentai.v1beta3.DocumentProcessorService.BatchProcessDocuments].

snippets.title: DocumentProcessorService reviewDocument Sample
snippets.description: Send a document for Human Review. The input document should be processed by the specified processor.

snippets.title: DocumentProcessorService evaluateProcessorVersion Sample
snippets.description: Evaluates a ProcessorVersion against annotated documents, producing an Evaluation.

snippets.title: DocumentProcessorService getEvaluation Sample
snippets.description: Retrieves a specific evaluation.

snippets.title: DocumentProcessorService listEvaluations Sample
snippets.description: Retrieves a set of evaluations for a given processor version.

snippets.title: DocumentProcessorService importProcessorVersion Sample
snippets.description: Imports a processor version from source processor version.

snippets.title: DocumentProcessorService updateDataset Sample
snippets.description: Updates metadata associated with a dataset.

snippets.title: DocumentProcessorService importDocuments Sample
snippets.description: Import documents into a dataset.

snippets.title: DocumentProcessorService getDocument Sample
snippets.description: Returns relevant fields present in the requested document.

snippets.title: DocumentProcessorService batchDeleteDocuments Sample
snippets.description: Deletes a set of documents.

snippets.title: DocumentProcessorService getDatasetSchema Sample
snippets.description: Gets the `DatasetSchema` of a `Dataset`.

snippets.title: DocumentProcessorService updateDatasetSchema Sample
snippets.description: Updates a `DatasetSchema`.
